verseObjects.content: + \ft Some ancient copies add, \fqa "We wanted to judge him according to our law \fqa* .
+ \ft Some ancient copies have verse 7, \fqa But Lysias, the officer, came and took him by force out of our hands \fqa* .
+ \ft Some ancient copies add to the first part of verse 8, \fqa commanding his accusers to come to you \fqa* as the end of the sentence begun in verse 7.
